# Your current login controller handles:

-> email + password → check DB → compare bcrypt → issue JWT

# OAuth flow is:

-> Google/GitHub login → provider gives user info → backend verifies → create/find user → issue your JWT

// --------- Big Picture Flow for file uploading to S3 -------- //

Frontend (FormData)
↓
Multer (memory storage)
↓
Upload to S3
↓
Get image URL
↓
Save URL in DB
